Photo, Ben Agajanian (left) takes notes and holder John Powers watches as 
soccer star Michelle Akers drives another one through the uprights during a 
recent place-kicking session at Millikan High in Long Beach. THOMAS KELSEY / 
Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
