</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A photograph in Saturday's Times of Fred Hayman, former owner of Giorgio 
Beverly Hills, was incorrectly identified as a photograph of movie executive 
Giancarlo Parretti. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
